org.apache.jackrabbit.core.cluster

Interface ClusterRecordProcessor

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ClusterNode

    public interface ClusterRecordProcessor
    Cluster record processor. Pass an implementation of this interface to a ClusterRecord and it will call back the appropriate process method.
    See Also:
    ClusterRecord.process(ClusterRecordProcessor)
